data.title: Bibi Gaytán
data.meta_description: Bibi Gaytán. Actress: Baila conmigo. Bibi has 4 brothers, she is the only girl, and grew up in Tabasco, Mexico. One day after her entire family moved to Mexico city, she went to audition for the group Timbiriche, out of a 100 auditioners she got the job, and performed with Timbiriche from 1989 to 1992. She was also part of the group Munecos De Papel which only lasted 3 months....
data.text: Has 5 children with her husband Eduardo Capetillo: a son Eduardo Capetillo, Jr. (b.1994), 2 daughters Ana Paula Capetillo (b.1997) & Alejandra Capetillo (b.1999), and twin sons Manuel Capetillo & Daniel Capetillo (b.June 20, 2014).
